Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:11.05,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fsp-1}翻譯：絆笑  Miya　校對：千葉命　後期：volence／阿爽/whwdlxy9416
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.20,0:00:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:54.53,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰かのためなら悪くはないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.77,0:01:00.37,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}理由らしいものは今日も　…見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:05.89,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}曖昧なリアル　点と点をつなぐ光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.24,0:01:12.63,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}消えそうな夢を　そっと握りしめてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:22.26,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}僕たちの声が  君の癒やせない傷痕に届けば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:27.86,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ナガレテク　雲の速さへと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:33.88,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}置いてかれないように叫ぶ　今日のエチュード
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:41.22,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}カナエタイ　静かな絶望の先に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:46.13,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}新しい　はじまりへのページ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:48.87,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その手をとって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:53.68,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}君が望むから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:57.14,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}どこまでも行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:54.53,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}若是為了誰  這無可厚非
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.77,0:01:00.37,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}今天依然沒看見像樣的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:05.89,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}曖昧交織的現實  點點相連的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.24,0:01:12.63,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嘗試著握住那轉眼即逝的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:22.26,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我們的聲音  若能傳達到你那無法治癒的傷痕的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:27.86,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}宛如流雲的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:33.88,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}為了不再置之不理  放聲唱出今天的練習曲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:41.22,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}渴望著那寂靜的絕望的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:46.13,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是通向全新伊始的篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:48.87,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}牽住你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:53.68,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}正如你所期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:57.14,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}一路向前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:12.08,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}路地裏には暗い暗い灯り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.37,0:22:16.56,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}そこに集う羽虫達のよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:20.77,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}もがく僕らは cry cry 共に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:25.25,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}秘めた思いをくすぶらせてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:29.92,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}「何をすればいい」　それがわからない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.13,0:22:34.27,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}無限の意味恐れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.48,0:22:38.58,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}しびれ切らした両の足が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:44.80,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}立ち上がれとせがんでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:51.27,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}全て運命だなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:53.41,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}神の落書きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:55.89,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}丸めて捨てるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:22:59.95,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}たったひとつの冴えたやり方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:04.13,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}いつも胸に抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.47,0:23:10.19,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}夜明け　睨みつけるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:12.08,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}小巷裏昏暗的燈光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.37,0:22:16.56,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}引得小飛蟲紛紛聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:20.77,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我們心急如焚一同哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:25.25,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}煽起深藏心中的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:29.92,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我不知該何去何從
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.13,0:22:34.27,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}無限的意義使我畏縮不前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.48,0:22:38.58,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}面對那失去知覺的雙腳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:44.80,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我央求道  快快站起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:51.27,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}一切都是命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:53.41,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只是神輕描淡寫的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:55.89,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}看我把它揉成一團一併扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:22:59.95,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}唯一行之有效的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:04.13,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}就是謹記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.47,0:23:10.19,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}怒視拂曉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TEXT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醬油拉麵一碗做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.82,0:00:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點醬油拉麵的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味噌拉麵也好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚通宵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…明老闆？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然說要通宵我實在…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海  還記得白天那位客人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在靠邊的啤酒箱上的那位  帶著墨鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來好像拉麵也沒吃幾口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.45,0:02:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是…今天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹽味拉麵  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味噌拉麵  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔥味拉麵  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是對我的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找上門的麻煩我奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用新作品讓他嘗嘗苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了明老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把菜刀拿開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了就快來準備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從改良湯頭開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島同學沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…不…也不能說沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經連續三天熬夜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能和我換班嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過幫忙做湯頭的話還是要讓你來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站…站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明老闆…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什…什麼打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛洗完澡  很正常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在吵什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:04:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這可沒啥可偷的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明老闆？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纏胸布被偷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即處以絞刑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就狠狠地揍他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位考慮問題怎麼那麼暴力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島中將  你這還算新人NEET嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來就不是NEET…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過幾年這裏就會成為你的歸處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是顯而易見的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花丸拉麵是我們NEET的聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是所謂的聖域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷走這裏的老大明老闆的內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無理之極  絕不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  哲哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯  能賒賬的只有這家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心話是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  來這麼多人是要幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於小偷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不和我們商量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事誰會開口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你的纏胸布被偷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就要靠無論是洗黑錢還是纏胸布大盜事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能順利解決的NEET偵探團集合全力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別集合全力來妨礙我做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  明老闆今天纏胸布的顏色變了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是第四次了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可能是跟蹤狂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很瞭解跟蹤狂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住女朋友家裏的時候  遇到過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在陪酒店或是特殊服務的店也經常…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這可是拉麵店  不是陪酒的也不是特殊服務的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  現在纏胸布被偷是事實吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以至於用剩下的門簾布頂替纏胸布
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是跟蹤狂麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明老闆  最近有沒有接到無聲電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}那不太可能吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信箱裏有被塞進什麼東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}那個也太誇張了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有感覺到背後有人跟著呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}再怎麼也不會做到那份上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來錯不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  明老闆？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  老闆  很久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有求與我的一天終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  變大的只有嘴上功夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹嘛  放我下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一點都沒成長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有好好吃東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我悄悄地多加了肉給你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙也有個限度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每人都有適合自己的體型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攝取蛋白質就會膨脹起來這種簡單的想法不可取
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明老闆去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明老闆昨晚以前纏胸布被偷在是什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,週四  那個墨鏡男來點了鹽味拉麵的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨鏡男是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次來都點不同的拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本不怎麼動筷子就走的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,週四墨鏡男來  纏胸布失竊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天墨鏡男來  纏胸布也失竊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨鏡男就是小偷麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我覺得那不太可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體型差別太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是共犯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲  攝像機的錄像呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒拍到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒拍到？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少沒拍到可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是事實  老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何既然是共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次墨鏡男出現的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有可能再次盜竊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍人之血久違地沸騰起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手都癢癢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加強店面周邊的防衛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓女孩們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想讓我的店倒閉麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法的事  畢竟她並沒有正式委託我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下嘛  還是讓他們調查下比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  委託愛麗絲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會把纏胸布拿去聞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定每天都會聞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡前醒來都聞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定大街上邊走邊聞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我委託你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我委託你可以了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿哲負責打聽客人和可疑人物的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿宏負責在車站附近收集情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐負責分析攝像機以及強化保安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你像往常一樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次入侵者出現的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒起作用的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了幫老闆打雜之外還能幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我回去咯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實店裏的客人也看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是像幽靈一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視攝像機方面呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒結果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可謂神出鬼沒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  吃點拉麵重整旗鼓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光…臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡麻拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡麻辣面  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然出了這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以彩夏在抓到犯人之前也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我無論如何都要去照看溫室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒法來打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過藤島同學還是擔心一下自己比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就是一副快掛掉的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被擺了一道  跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在附近再找找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我向愛麗絲和明老闆報告一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏哥剛才聯繫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後還是失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試喝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道不怎麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺一股海藻味  不像拉麵的湯底了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這鍋湯底也不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜那位客人可能想吃老爸的拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這鍋湯底是…你父親的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模仿而已  模仿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸也沒想過我會繼承這家店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒問過配料表
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我一直在叛逆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計他都放棄這家店和我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是入侵者今晚出現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒計劃已經完備了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且老闆家的保安也進行了強化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲  關於這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個玄關的鎖絕對不可以動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼老式的鎖只要想撬誰都能撬開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了強化保安只能將它換掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明老闆無論如何都不同意換
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不早報告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨鏡男和竊賊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有拒絕更換舊鎖的老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白些什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門鎖這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆警戒  引誘犯人行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時我會動員僅有的一點勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏出這座堡壘  親自用雙手去確認
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了把真相化為事實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏哥哲哥已就位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也盡快回到崗位上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…我要去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島中將負責室內的警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人要是出現了就用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是誘餌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你再逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好  藤島中將
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向井均特製閃光彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這是在擾鄰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉迷於你的纏胸布氣味的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是我這個偵探的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿宏  他的身份是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木村富雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HIS  ANGELICA的開發部部長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  是個大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HIS  ANGELICA是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是知名女性內衣製造商
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎是那裏的設計師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木村富雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要偷纏胸布
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能忍受她使用纏胸布
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纏胸布根本就不是內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是藝術家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真理的探求者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我光是用看的就能知道女性內衣的尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光用看的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是被上帝選中的人才擁有的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想的內衣可以襯托女性的身段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性的胴體可以讓內衣閃亮發光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造就這究極之美正是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掌握了你的胸圍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下胸圍70上胸圍95的G罩杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這在我們業界是被稱為泰姬瑪哈陵般的奇跡形狀的人間至寶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:17:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種奇跡般的胸竟然被纏胸布束縛住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是褻瀆上帝的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了讓你開竅連照片都發你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須穿戴我這個藝術家所設計的內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你的遺言是不是就這些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆  我沒打算阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不認為在得知事件真相後再動手也不遲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木村富雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有一件事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關於你侵入時所見到的一個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我換個問法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是如何侵入這間屋子的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因…因為玄關的鎖就是開著的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明上鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖是開著的  老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他每天都監視著這間屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而某天他看見某個人光明正大地打開玄關的門進入屋內
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就從沒有上鎖的門潛入這間屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他認為那個人是這間房子的住戶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我們則認為他是你的同夥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我們都錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎麼回事  愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好說明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆  你拒絕了換門鎖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的選擇是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…可是事到如今才回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…明老闆也在等嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等令尊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  要是不狠狠揍他一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這氣就沒地方消啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在去店裏說不定就能找到答案哦  老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人有兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人都是單獨行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前放跑的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後突破我們重重包圍網的墨鏡男子是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花田勝  老闆的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她爸爸是來做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在老闆應該在聆聽生者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒想像中好喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純粹是來嘲笑我的拉麵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一聲不吭地就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是回來了也至少說句話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次回來的時候讓我嘗嘗你的冰激凌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.74,0:20:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了  不管怎麼想他都是消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為你的動態視力只對女性有效吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這只是推測
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能避開監控攝像機
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不被察覺的情況下掌握拍攝範圍並快速通過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到這點的絕非凡人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再綜合宏哥的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說他在特殊機關接受過訓練嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還做了整容手術回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.69,0:20:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼明老闆會察覺不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是親生女兒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要否定就拿別的假設推翻我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊  來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是今早在店裏發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們覺得是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你真的不管什麼尺寸都看得出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.75,0:21:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是飛機場也沒問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  根據情況今天倒不是不能放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說愛麗絲那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在愚弄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我像老闆那樣長肉來配合這個尺寸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是掛在門上…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個又惡劣又不知羞恥又無禮的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說這是誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點  愛麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}NEET偵探事務所  愛麗絲小姐收
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.41,0:23:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第四代舉辦的活動上幫忙的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.56,0:23:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能勝任候選負責人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.86,0:23:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了危險卻又不可思議的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
